snippet.title: Dual Universe Kickstarter Video
snippet.description:
Following our successful Kickstarter campaign and popular demand, we developed a new crowdfunding website that allows more players to participate. More info here: http://www.dualthegame.com/crowdfunding

Dual Universe is a continuous Single-Shard sandbox MMORPG taking place in a multi-planets Sci-Fi world with player-driven in-game economy, politics, trade and warfare. Players can freely modify the world by creating structures, space ships or orbital stations, giving birth to empires and civilizations. Support our Kicksrater campaign! 
 
Stay tuned! 

Official website: http://www.dualthegame.com

Join the community:
- on our forum: https://board.dualthegame.com
- on our community portal: https://community.dualthegame.com/

Follow us on:
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/dualuniverse
- Twitter: https://twitter.com/dualuniverse
- Google+: https://plus.google.com/+DualUniverse
- Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/dualuniverse
